Sentencas: The relationships between the cathode performance, the La(0.6)Sr(0.4)Co(0.2)Fe(0.8)O(3-delta) (LSCF)/Ag ratios, and the porosity of the LSCF-Ag cermet cathode were investigated.
Titulo: LSCF-Ag Cermet Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The Ag fractions in the LSCF-Ag powder were changed from 20 to 80 wt %.
Titulo: LSCF-Ag Cermet Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The microstructures of the porous LSCF-Ag cermet cathodes were observed using a scanning electron microscope, and the area specific resistance of the cathodes was measured by the two-probe ac impedance method.
Titulo: LSCF-Ag Cermet Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The LSCF-Ag cermet cathodes with different Ag fractions annealed at 750 degrees C for 3 h had the optimum microstructure and the lowest Rp when the Ag fraction in the LSCF-Ag cermet cathodes was 40 or 50 wt %, and the LSCF-Ag cermet cathode including 50 wt % Ag had a sufficient porosity without the poly(methyl methacrylate).
Titulo: LSCF-Ag Cermet Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
